  "local_port": 56232,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are the best Magento pop up extensions out there? Both free and paid?",
  "response": "When you're looking for Magento pop-up extensions, there are several options available, both free and paid, depending on your specific needs like features, ease of use, and customization capabilities. Here are some popular Magento pop-up extensions:\n\n### Paid Extensions\n\n1. **Mageplaza Popup**:\n   - **Features**: Highly customizable designs, targeting rules, exit intent popups, and A/B testing capabilities.\n   - **Benefits**: Responsive design, integration with Google Analytics for performance tracking, and user-friendly interface.\n\n2. **Amasty Popup Pro**:\n   - **Features**: Variety of display options, precise targeting settings, and scheduling capabilities.\n   - **Benefits**: Drag-and-drop editor, mobile-friendly, and ability to display coupons and subscription forms.\n\n3. **Aheadworks Popup Pro**:\n   - **Features**: Customizable pop-up templates, time-based triggers, and behavioral targeting.\n   - **Benefits**: Enhanced customer engagement tools, integration capability with email marketing services, and detailed analytics.\n\n4. **Landofcoder Popup**:\n   - **Features**: Allows flexible rules for displaying pop-ups, supports various content types such as video and HTML, and multiple trigger options.\n   - **Benefits**: Responsive design, rule-based targeting, and detailed reports.\n\n### Free Extensions\n\n1. **Magebuzz Popup**:\n   - **Features**: Basic popup functionality to engage visitors with promotions or newsletter subscriptions.\n   - **Benefits**: Easy to set up, and offers a simple way to increase sign-ups without cost.\n\n2. **Magesolutions Pop-up Manager**:\n   - **Features**: Create and manage popup windows efficiently with a range of display options.\n   - **Benefits**: Intuitive interface and supports essential popup functions for small businesses.\n\n3. **FMEextensions Free Popup Extension**:\n   - **Features**: Basic popup features with responsive design, focused on newsletter subscription forms.\n   - **Benefits**: Easy to configure and ideal for websites looking to capture emails.\n\nWhen selecting a pop-up extension, consider your specific requirement for customization, budget, and the overall user experience you want to offer on your online store. Always check recent reviews and ensure compatibility with your current Magento version before installation.",
